metadata.name: Ignis Fatuus
metadata.description:
Huleeb's artworks have a very cohesive universe and theme. For our collaboration, we used our colours to create a light effect for them to integrate properly with Huleeb's monochromatic creation.

A colourful ray of light emanates from the head of the faceless character towards the tree it holds in his hands, as an ode to the fragility and power of nature.
